com.lgc.wsh.util
Class IndexGrouper

java.lang.Object
  com.lgc.wsh.util.IndexGrouper

public class IndexGrouper
extends java.lang.Object

Arrange a sorted set of indices into groups of like elements. This works well after IndexSorter or with RecursiveArraySorter. Implement the IndexGrouper.Grouper interface to identify whether adjacent indices are in the same group or not.
